	<h3>Related Documents</h3>      
	<ul>
	
	<li><a href="/en/employment/employment_rights_and_conditions/hours_of_work/working_week.html">The working week</a><br>The maximum working hours for most employees are set out in the Organisation of Working Time Act 1997.</li>
	
	<li><a href="/en/employment/starting_work_and_changing_job/young_people_at_work/hours_of_work_for_young_people.html">Hours of work for young people</a><br>The working hours for children and young people are regulated by legislation which sets maximum working hours and rest intervals.</li>
	
	<li><a href="/en/employment/employment_rights_and_conditions/hours_of_work/rest_periods_and_breaks.html">Rest periods and breaks</a><br>Employees are entitled to breaks during work and rest between periods of working time.</li>
	
